# 🌐 Chaotic Admin Console – Master Feature List

## 🧩 UNIFIED ADMIN CONSOLE
- Single React UI (Dashboard, Admin Panel, Grid, AI)
- Sidebar navigation
- Responsive design (mobile-friendly)
- Dark mode theme with cyan branding

## 📊 MOBILE DASHBOARD
- Live restart countdown
- Grid overview: name, type, player count, status color

## 🛠 ADMIN PANEL
- Grid selection A1–E5
- Start / Stop server buttons (via `.bat`)
- RCON broadcast to selected grid
- Load / view `config.json`

## 🗺 GRID VISUALIZER
- Interactive 5x5 ATLAS map
- Status via RCON port checks
- Tooltip with role + player count

## 🧠 AI LOG ANALYZER
- Scans 25 grid log folders
- Detects fatal errors, OOM, assert fails
- Summarizes issues in plain English
- Extendable for Discord/web alerts

## 🖥 ELECTRON GUI + AUTO-UPDATER
- `.exe` version of the console
- System tray icon, launch + Flask backend
- Auto-updates via GitHub Releases

## 🚀 GITHUB ACTIONS CI
- Builds `.exe` + `.Setup.exe` when you push a tag (e.g. `v1.0.0`)
- Publishes files to GitHub Releases

## 🧰 DEV TOOLS & STRUCTURE
- `/client/`, `/server/`, `/data/`, `/dist/`, `main.js`, `package.json`
- Local test server and overlay system
- JSON auto-sync + restart tool
